015aaka Era |date=1988 |publisher=[[Universit\u00e9 catholique de Louvain]], Institut orientaliste |isbn=90-683-1-100-X |language=fr |orig-year=1958}}\n* {{Citation |last1=Lee |first1=S.L. |title=Surviving Nirvana: Death of the Buddha in Chinese Visual Culture |date=2010 |publisher=[[Hong Kong University Press]] |isbn=978-962-209-125-2}}\n* {{Citation |last1=MacQueen |first1=Graeme |editor1-last=Williams |editor1-first=Paul |title=Buddhism: Critical Concepts in Religious Studies, 3: The Origins and Nature of Mah\u0101y\u0101na Buddhism |date=2005 |orig-year=1981{{en dash}}2 |publisher=[[Routledge]] |chapter=Inspired Speech in Early Mah\u0101y\u0101na Buddhism |isbn=0-415-33229-X |pages=312\u2013343}}\n* {{Citation |last1=Malalasekera|author-link= G P Malalasekera|first1=G.P.|title=Dictionary of P\u0101li Proper Names|year=1937 |publisher=[[Pali Text Society]] |oclc=837021145|url=http://www.palikanon.com/english/pali_names/dic_idx.html}}\n* {{Citation|last1=Migot|first1=A. |author-link=Andr\u00e9 Migot|title=Un grand disciple du Buddha: S\u0101riputra. Son r\u00f4le dans l'histoire du bouddhisme et dans le d\u00e9veloppement de l'Abhidharma|trans-title=A great disciple of the Buddha: S\u0101riputra, his role in Buddhist history and in the development of Abhidharma|journal=Bulletin de l'\u00c9cole fran\u00e7aise d'Extr\u00eame-Orient |date=1954|volume=46|issue=2|doi=10.3406/befeo.1954.5607|url=http://www.persee.fr/docAsPDF/befeo_0336-1519_1954_num_46_2_5607.pdf|language=fr}}\n* {{Citation |last=Minayev |first=I.P. |author-link=Ivan Minayev |year=1894 |title=Recherches sur le bouddhisme |publisher=Ernest Leroux |oclc=25136566 |language=fr |trans-title=Studies in Buddhism |url=https://archive.org/download/recherchessurleb00mina/recherchessurleb00mina.pdf |others=(originally in Russian)}}\n* {{Citation |last1=Morrison |first1=E. |title=The Power of Patriarchs: Qisong and Lineage in Chinese Buddhism |date=2010 |publisher=[[Brill Publishing]] |isbn=978-90-04-18301-8}}\n* {